      "versionNonce": 1306140523,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1731013445335,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- It makes you think like a developer (when using it to the fullest capabilities)\n  - Dev mode\n  - Variants\n  - Auto Layout\n  - Constraints\n  - Design Systems (https://bradfrost.com/blog/post/design-systems-are-for-user-interfaces/ 2021)\n    - Components (https://bradfrost.com/blog/post/atomic-web-design/ 2013!)\n      - HTML (1991)\n        - HTML 2 (1994)\n        - HTML 3 (1997)\n        - HTML 4 (1997)\n        - HTML 5 (2014) - 5.2 (2017)\n      - BEM (2010) yandex\\*\n      - AngularJS (2010) google\n      - Atmoic design (2013) brad frost\n      - React (2013) facebook\n      - Vue (2014) evan you\n      - ITCSS (2014) csswizardry\\*\n      - Angular (2016) google\n      - Figma (2016) -> 2017 Components",
      "fontSize": 50.06596274006087,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- It makes you think like a developer (when using it to the fullest capabilities)\n  - Dev mode\n  - Variants\n  - Auto Layout\n  - Constraints\n  - Design Systems (https://bradfrost.com/blog/post/design-systems-are-for-user-interfaces/ 2021)\n    - Components (https://bradfrost.com/blog/post/atomic-web-design/ 2013!)\n      - HTML (1991)\n        - HTML 2 (1994)\n        - HTML 3 (1997)\n        - HTML 4 (1997)\n        - HTML 5 (2014) - 5.2 (2017)\n      - BEM (2010) yandex\\*\n      - AngularJS (2010) google\n      - Atmoic design (2013) brad frost\n      - React (2013) facebook\n      - Vue (2014) evan you\n      - ITCSS (2014) csswizardry\\*\n      - Angular (2016) google\n      - Figma (2016) -> 2017 Components",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
